ERA One Source Realty - Lake Ariel

data.description: Looking for a home that is completely move in ready?  Look no further.  This bi-level home has just been completely re-done from top to bottom.  All the expensive changes have been made.  New roof, new gutters, new septic system, new garage door, brand new kitchen with high end finishes, farm sink, and appliances.  Main living area has been opened up to enjoy open concept living at its finest.  All new flooring & lighting throughout.  All 3 bathrooms have been updated.  Heating system was converted to propane, a new pellet stove and a tankless on demand water heater installed.  The exterior has all new doors, new shutters, light fixtures, a freshly painted deck and gravel added to the driveway.  The electrical and plumbing have been updated as well.  Enjoy the peaceful setting on this 1.52 acre property but also close to everything.  Only a ten minute drive to I84, I81 and the Casey Hwy.  House is located on a private dead end street so there is no traffic.  Schedule your showing today!
